{"tid":1548013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【核彈】美國傳媒深入調查供港催淚彈嘅當地軍火製造商","createTime":"2019-09-07T01:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T02:08:35.000Z","uid":296674,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9a9740bd25d1e5e37f86f32105e4ae1b44083afe","tid":1548013,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:30:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/rosalindadams/tear-gas-hong-kong-made-in-usa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeednews.com%2Farticle%2Frosalindadams%2Ftear-gas-hong-kong-made-in-usa&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=0500777a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/rosalindadams/tear-gas-hong-kong-made-in-usa</a><br />\n<br />\nBuzzfeed News係美國嘅立場新聞<br />\n佢地揭發呢個位於賓夕法尼亞州鄉郊嘅軍火製造商<br />\n用僅僅高於最低工資兩美元嘅價錢聘請員工<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">係貨櫃入面</span></strong>製造催淚彈<br />\n輸出<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港、土耳其、巴林、埃及</span></strong>用嚟暴力鎮壓爭取民主嘅示威<br />\n<br />\n呢間軍火製造商非同小可，置人命如草芥<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">多次違反勞工部安全指引 壓榨員工</span></strong><br />\n連老闆自己都比化學物嚴重燒傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>呢篇文章講解催淚彈嘅製作過程，以及所構成嘅嚴重職業安全風險<br />\n仲唔快啲做文宣 要求美國商務部介入 撤銷所有武器輸出牌照 保護我哋嘅手足<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"651dc31718b41e1fc3fa0991156b387667a7ad6f","tid":1548013,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:30:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eceb4282848e8ec75aae6c62957dbcaea0b385ce","tid":1548013,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:31:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0ca52952e39fcaab4c5a5603cd217b8083f0d14","tid":1548013,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd96dd21d1e5f36e7a93000643bac1f7fdbf396","tid":1548013,"uid":2874